snippet.title: Minecraft x Angry Birds DLC – Official Trailer
snippet.description: Are you seeing RED? The Bad Piggies are up to their old tricks in a brand new setting –  Minecraft. Fling yourself into the Angry Birds adventure map to rescue the birds’ eggs, unlock RED’s friends and new missions, and snag Red’s Hoodie now available for free in the Dressing Room! https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=8d017abf-734e-4767-be02-22b1c815e3f7
